headline: Capital One Financial Corporation (COF): A Bull Case Theory
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on Capital One Financial Corporation (COF) on Substack by Stock Analysis Compilation. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on COF. Capital One Financial Corporation (COF)’s share was trading at $175.66 as of Dec 19th. COF’s trailing and forward P/E were 16.59 and 11.52 respectively according to Yahoo Finance. […]
